wiki.gravisuit.preview.gravisuit_tools.d: Gravisuit adds a few useful tools, like the relocator and gravitool. You can find info on them here.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.gravisuit_armor.d: Here you can find information on Gravisuit jetpacks and lappacks.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.gravitool.desc: The Gravitool is an all in one hoe, wrench, treetap, and screwdriver. No longer do you need 3 different tools in your toolbox/hotbar, now you can have just 1!
wiki.gravisuit.preview.relocator.desc: The Relocator is an upgrade to the teleporter with 3 different modes: Personal - Right click opens a gui with up to 10 different teleport locations, shift right click to add a location. Translocator - Sends an orb that teleports an entity it hits to the default teleport location, shift right click to set the default teleport location. Portal - Spawns a portal that teleports whatever enters it to the default teleport location, lasts 25 seconds. Shift right click to set default location.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.vajra.desc: The Vajra is an advanced mining tool that allows you to mine at creative speed with right click, and even faster with left click. It can also enable silk touch.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.magnet.desc: The Magnet is a tool that will, depending on the mode, either instantly pickup items you mine or attract items dropped in the area to you.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.voider.desc: The Voider is a tool that will void items set in the filter in the gui automatically when you pick them up.
The Advanced Lappack and Ultimate Lappack are better versions of the lappack and quantum pack respectively.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.advanced_electric: The advanced electric jetpacks are better versions of the electric jetpack, with a max height of 278.
wiki.gravisuit.preview.gravitation_jetpa: The gravitation jetpack is top tier jetpack that allows one to use creative flight, press g to activate.
